snippet.title: Diana is going to swim in the pool. Dad explains how to swim properly
snippet.description:
Diana is going to swim in the pool. Dad explains how to swim properly, what to wear and what to take with you. Diana and Roma with their parents go to the water park and have fun together!
Thanks for watching!
